<PAGE TITLE="Menu Entries" SUBTITLE="Remote Link" PARENT=":menu/index.html" KEYWORDS="Menu,Idle,Remote Link,Connect,Idle">

<HEADING>Remote Link</HEADING>
<PARA>
Selecting the <MENL TITLE="Remote Link"> menu entry initiates a connection to a remote <SIBO> or <EPOC> device using the <PLP> with the <A HREF=":menu/confg.html" TITLE="Configure...">configured</A> serial block driver and baud rate. The <A HREF=":icon/act.html" TITLE="Remote Link Icon">remote link icon</A> is displayed to indicate the new state.
<P>
This has the same effect as clicking on the <A HREF=":icon/idle.html" TITLE="Idle Icon">idle icon</A> with <MOUSE BUTTON=SELECT>.
</PARA>

</PAGE>
